The paper deals with compressed sensing and recovery from multiple measurements, which are topics that fall under the sub-categories of Information Theory (cs.IT), Signal Processing (cs.SP), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The use of algorithms and analysis of their performance suggest Numerical Analysis (cs.NA) as another possible sub-category. Finally, the mention of joint-sparse recovery and the ReMBo algorithm suggest that the paper could also belong to the sub-category of Multimedia (cs.MM).
